ision turned parts, including bar-route shaft components, injector assembly parts, and power steering assemblies; and precision machined castings products, as well as precision products for control valves. It serves agricultural, compressor, defense, commercial, and off highway clients, as well as diesel engines, cars, and LCVs/HCVs. The company also exports its products. Menon Pistons Limited was founded in 1969 and is based in Kolhapur, India."}}